title: Rezo Gavtadze
text:
Rezo Davidovich Gavtadze (; born 11 July 1995) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player of <a href="Georgians">Georgian</a> origin who plays as a <a href="left%20midfielder">left midfielder</a> for <a href="FC%20Chikhura%20Sachkhere">FC Chikhura Sachkhere</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut on 19 March 2016 for <a href="FC%20Ural%20Sverdlovsk%20Oblast">FC Ural Sverdlovsk Oblast</a> in a <a href="Russian%20Football%20Premier%20League">Russian Football Premier League</a> game against <a href="FC%20Terek%20Grozny">FC Terek Grozny</a>.
